{"tid":2451850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界維吾爾大會促美國要求中國關閉新疆再教育營","createTime":"2021-03-18T11:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T11:41:49.000Z","uid":189046,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8540922c492acdad8a6b64ab885302c66bc045f5","tid":2451850,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"世界維吾爾大會促美國要求中國關閉新疆再教育營 <br />\n<br />\n世界維吾爾大會去信美國國務卿布林肯，敦促他稍後在阿拉斯加與中方高層官員面時，要求中方立即關閉在新疆的再教育營，無條件釋放被任意拘留的人，並結束強迫勞動，容許聯合國派員調查。大會主席伊薩表示，最重要是中國必須無條件結束對東突厥斯坦，即新疆正進行的種族滅絕及反人類罪行。 中國常駐聯合國日內瓦代表陳旭，日前在聯合國人權理事會會議上指，新疆及西藏繁榮穩定，各族人民安居樂業，要將種族滅絶的帽子扣到中國頭上，荒謬至極，絶不可能得逞。 到星期三，歐盟成員國大使同意，就中國嚴重侵犯新疆維吾爾族的人權，制裁中國官員，等成員國外長下周一開會通過後，才公佈被制裁官員及實體的名單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2383599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2383599&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2WWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=9d36e966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2383599</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ec390085a94857eb3ae8d3530ad9c453e09ed9","tid":2451850,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"阿美利叻合眾國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PP9oFTW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPP9oFTW.jpg&h=d26abb1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d989a5c3cbe6c8b0ffacaebae3616ef41a5ad07e","tid":2451850,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/12/A4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FA4.jpeg&h=1ad4793a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/IVkxzDfhBYK9Lbu58ixHIQ--~B/aD0xMDgwO3c9MTYyMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--